#   livecoding environment (Sonic Pi, TidalCycles, FoxDot, ORCA,
#   Symbolic Composer, Common Music, SuperCollider, Pure Data,
#   Max/MSP), every hardware sequencer (Arturia BeatStep Pro,
#   Polyend Tracker, Squarp Pyramid, Elektron Octatrack /
#   Digitone / Digitakt / Syntakt, Akai MPC, Roland TR-8S /
#   TR-6S, KORG SQ-64, M-Audio Code 49 / 61), every drum
#   machine (KORG Volca, Behringer RD-9 / RD-8, Roland TR-808 /
#   909 / 707), every MIDI controller (Akai APC, Novation
#   Launchpad / Launchkey, Native Instruments Maschine, Ableton
#   Push, M-Audio Hammer 88), every guitar-to-MIDI converter
